Usage: spaceman.scraper {`Nt`: `V#s.`corp.script}

T1 Debug functions:
[Deprecated] `Ndebug`:`V"t1"` Displays all of the below
`Ndebug`:`Vtrue` Displays corp arg info
`Np_debug`: `Vtrue` Returns project locs with their corresponding projects
`Nscreen`: `Vtrue` || `V"raw"` Returns the decorrupted or raw corp info screen
`Ncmdscreen`: `Vtrue` || `V"raw"` Returns the decorrupted or raw cmd info screen
`Ndescription`: `Vtrue` Returns the corp's description page
